      "comment": "ROSEWOOD REBEL (1) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 5th at this track in Grade 5 company. Has a good record here at this journey. Better than last start and worth following up. BELLVIEW ACES (2) ran below her best last time finishing seventh (17.14) over 300m at this track in a Grade 5. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Cannot be taken lightly. STAYING ALIVE (6) has a strong record this trip with four wins and three placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (16.72) when seventh over 300m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. TUTA LONGEVITY (3) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
